## ‚ú® Features

### UI & Layout
- Transparent navigation bar
- Full-screen hero section with background image
- Fully responsive design (desktop, tablet, mobile)

### Product Gallery
- Left & right arrow navigation
- Clickable thumbnail images
- Smooth image transition animation
- Active thumbnail highlighting

### Subscription Selection
- Single Subscription & Double Subscription options
- Only one subscription box expands at a time
- Smooth expand and collapse animation
- Visual fragrance selection

### Dynamic Add to Cart
- Add-to-cart link updates dynamically
- Based on selected:
  - Fragrance
  - Purchase type

### Scroll-Based Animations
- Percentage counters animate on scroll
- Section reveal animations using IntersectionObserver
- Optimized for performance

### Accordion Section
- One accordion open at a time
- Clean toggle interaction

### Comparison Table
- Built using pure HTML `<table>`
- Highlighted GTG column
- Responsive with horizontal scroll on small screens

